35
00:01:52,930 --> 00:01:58,560
I'm afraid they are coming after us.

36
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:04,949
But who is so bold as to go against us?

37
00:02:04,949 --> 00:02:07,290
Except for Xiao Jinyu and his people,

38
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:10,990
who else dares to go

39
00:02:10,990 --> 00:02:15,810
against me like this in Chang'an?

40
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:21,139
Do you mean it's the group of people under the banner of Duke Chang?

41
00:02:21,139 --> 00:02:24,579
But why would they go against you?

42
00:02:24,579 --> 00:02:27,519
What are they up to?

43
00:02:27,519 --> 00:02:31,350
They are under the banner of Duke Chang now.

44
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:35,259
What do you think they are up to?

45
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:38,930
The vast lands of Tang?

46
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:41,170
Land?

47
00:02:41,170 --> 00:02:44,349
Master, since the An Shi Rebellion,

48
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:48,629
the emperors come and go, but the Division of Eunuchs is always here.

49
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:50,960
No matter who ascends the throne

50
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,960
we are still the ones in charge.

51
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:58,889
I think you have lived a life of ease for too long.

52
00:02:58,889 --> 00:03:02,190
You don't even know what death means.

53
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:04,929
