54
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:10,400
Our heads might fall off our necks anytime.

55
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,160
Do you understand?

56
00:03:16,830 --> 00:03:21,329
Listen. Get your act together.

57
00:03:21,329 --> 00:03:25,020
Someone will come to us soon.

58
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:26,119
Yes.

59
00:03:26,119 --> 00:03:29,459
That's all you can say. Idiot! Idiot!

60
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:34,710
Master, watch your hands.

61
