62
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:48,620
[Episode 27]

63
00:04:01,550 --> 00:04:03,679
Don't cry out. Be quiet.

64
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:06,269
I'm afraid she is clumsy and she will singe my skin.

65
