Your skin is thick enough. It won't hurt to singe it a little bit.

66
00:04:18,050 --> 00:04:20,550
There are burn marks.

67
00:04:20,550 --> 00:04:21,919
This is the bark of beech willow.

68
00:04:21,919 --> 00:04:23,859
Put it on the skin and bake it over a fire,

69
