582
00:35:21,580 --> 00:35:24,980
[List]

583
00:35:31,350 --> 00:35:34,020
Secretary in charge of the military supplies.

584
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:39,569
He should be the one who can contact the people of the local office most frequently, right?

585
00:35:39,569 --> 00:35:42,940
Yes. Are you suspecting him?

586
00:35:44,240 --> 00:35:45,629
It's impossible.

587
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:48,759
Although he is in charge of buying supplies, he has no power to deploy troops.

588
00:35:48,759 --> 00:35:51,219
He reports these things to General Leng.

589
